		<description><![CDATA[<p>The Age Of Innovation And The Chief Technology Officer The digital era has created a plethora of threats, risks, values and opportunities for organizations. However, until recently, there has not been a dedicated position in organizations to truly harness the rise of digital technologies. Enter, the Chief Technology Officer. Takeaway food stores weren’t looking for &#8230;</p>
